725645f-a.title: Queens: 77th Avenue - Parsons Boulevard
725645f-a.text:
77th Avenue, at east side of Parsons Boulevard, showing
new frame houses under construction on both sides of the
avenue. Parsons Boulevard is in the foregPound. This area
was formerly occupied by farms.
P. L. Sperr  March 23, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS
